###############
### VCP-CMA ### 
###############

*** Automation - faster resource provisioning, more consistency, minimization of human error, scalability
          vRA (vRealize Automation) - automates the provisioning of IT infrastructure, with/without Self Service, including approval chain

*** Components
          Cloud Assembly - assembles VMs/Instances into Blueprint
          Service Broker - creates self-service catalog
          Code Stream

*** Architecture
          
